<plot>Neeru dances in her bedroom by herself dreaming of becoming a famous Bollywood actress. The problem? She lives in suburbia, far away from the lights, sounds and color of Bollywood. While her parents try to set her up with a 'nice Indian boy', Neeru's dreams don't allow her settle down for too long. What develops is a hilarious and touching film about taking risks and living your dreams - no matter how crazy they are.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?078202</url></doc>
